description: Stunning waterfront PENTHOUSE with private roof terrace. 3 BEDROOMS with en suite bathrooms and a fabulous DEN located in Pier 4, the Seaport's luxury boutique building. Private 14' balcony,low voltage lighting and sound system & floor to ceiling glass windows with electric blinds compliment the spacious open kitchen/living/dining room. The gourmet kitchen has an expansive marble counters & waterfall island w/seating and Gaggenau/Bosch appliances including a 5 burner gas range,steam oven & 99 bottle wine refrigerator. The luxurious primary suite is comprised of a full wall custom built in and two custom closets complemented by an en suite bathroom with marble shower, separate water closet and double vanities. High end finishes include electric blinds, wide plank walnut floors and ceilings up to 10'4". Direct access from  the living room is a private Roof Terrace with stainless steel kitchen comprised of a gas grill, refrigerator, sink, ice maker, island with bar seating and gas firepit
